    "• Approximate forgetting.",
    "A forgetting algorithm F (D f, A(D)) provides an approximate forgetting guarantee, if",
    "for an acceptable threshold t. Nguyen et al provide a definition for ϵ-certified forgetting, inspired by differential privacy.",
